stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    state "Validation Pending" as ValidationPending
    state "Duplicate Detected" as DuplicateDetected
    [*] --> Draft: Health worker starts registration
    Draft --> ValidationPending: Health worker submits the data
    ValidationPending --> DuplicateDetected: Matching record is found
    ValidationPending --> Validated: No matching record is found
    Validated --> Registered: System saves the patient record
    DuplicateDetected --> [*]: Health worker links or cancels the record
    Registered --> [*]: Registration completes
